#: ../../mattermost.rst:13
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr ""

#: ../../mattermost.rst:15
msgid ""
"Mattermost needs a dedicated virtual host, a FQDN like "
"``chat.nethserver.org``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../mattermost.rst:17
msgid ""
"Before proceeding with the configuration, make sure to create the "
"corresponding name record inside your DNS server. If you are planning to "
"use a Let's Encrypt certificate as default, make also sure to have a "
"corresponding public DNS record."
msgstr ""

#: ../../mattermost.rst:22
msgid ""
"Please note that the mobile app **cannot connect to servers with self-"
"signed certificates**!"
msgstr ""

#: ../../mattermost.rst:24
msgid "How to configure:"
msgstr ""

